EBM TECHNOLOGIES said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 46.25% to NT$7,877,000 from NT$14,656,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             7,877            14,656    
YOY%             -46.25%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales             44,667           39,756    
YOY%              12.35% 
=================================================================
 